{"data": [{"id": "4743509", "title": "Community Healthcare Trust: 10% Yield Gets Bullish Diagnosis, Few Side Effects Expected", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/896897324/image_896897324.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Japanese Medical System at clinic\" data-id=\"896897324\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/896897324/image_896897324.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/896897324/image_896897324.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/896897324/image_896897324.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/896897324/image_896897324.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/896897324/image_896897324.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/896897324/image_896897324.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/896897324/image_896897324.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/896897324/image_896897324.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Yoshiyoshi Hirokawa</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Portfolio Sector: REITs</h2> <p>The next article in my ongoing series called <em>The Future Investor</em> takes portfolio diversification further by exploring the world of REITs, specifically those that invest in properties for the medical sector, such as </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/896897324/image_896897324.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743509-community-healthcare-trust-10-percent-yield-gets-bullish-diagnosis-with-few-side-effects-expected", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 13:04:26"}, {"id": "4743508", "title": "Sirius XM's Strategy Shift Reveals Its Struggles", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439682718/image_1439682718.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Man drinking juice in inflatable ring\" data-id=\"1439682718\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439682718/image_1439682718.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439682718/image_1439682718.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439682718/image_1439682718.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439682718/image_1439682718.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439682718/image_1439682718.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439682718/image_1439682718.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439682718/image_1439682718.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439682718/image_1439682718.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">Will Sirius XM install satellite radios in inflatable pool ride-ons to delight its affluent subscriber base?</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>A surprising strategy shift</h2> <p>Yesterday, Sirius XM (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SIRI\" title=\"Sirius XM Holdings Inc.\">SIRI</a></span>) released an important <a href=\"https://investor.siriusxm.com/news-events/press-releases/detail/2129/siriusxm-provides-update-on-strategic-direction-sharpening\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://investor.siriusxm.com/news-events/press-releases/detail/2129/siriusxm-provides-update-on-strategic-direction-sharpening\" target=\"_blank\">strategy update</a>:</p> <blockquote><p>As 90% of SiriusXM's subscribers have the service embedded in-car</p></blockquote>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439682718/image_1439682718.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743508-sirius-xm-stock-strategy-shift-reveals-its-struggles", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 12:57:15"}, {"id": "4743505", "title": "Grab Holdings: So Many Bullish Catalysts Ahead", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Data analytics automated with AI technology. Big data, business analytics and artificial intelligence automation. Dashboard report with sales and operations charts and KPI insights on touch screen.\" data-id=\"2096475191\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">NicoElNino</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>Grab Holdings (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GRAB\" title=\"Grab Holdings Limited\">GRAB</a></span>) are building a superapp in Southeast Asia. They operate across delivery, and mobility - similar to Uber Technologies (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UBER\" title=\"Uber Technologies, Inc.\">UBER</a>) - and digital financial services - similar to PayPal (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PYPL\" title=\"PayPal Holdings, Inc.\">PYPL</a>) and SoFi</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743505-grab-holdings-so-many-bullish-catalysts-ahead", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 12:32:52"}, {"id": "4743504", "title": "Vale: Addressing The Short-Term Struggles", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1213898038/image_1213898038.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Panorama of iron ore quarry on a sunny day\" data-id=\"1213898038\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1213898038/image_1213898038.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1213898038/image_1213898038.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1213898038/image_1213898038.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1213898038/image_1213898038.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1213898038/image_1213898038.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1213898038/image_1213898038.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1213898038/image_1213898038.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1213898038/image_1213898038.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Maksym Isachenko/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Vale (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VALE\" title=\"Vale S.A.\">VALE</a></span>) is a standout among iron ore producers based on its almost unique ability to enjoy an operational advantage as a low-cost iron ore producer, which allows the company to remain profitable even</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1213898038/image_1213898038.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743504-vale-addressing-the-short-term-struggles", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 12:29:23"}, {"id": "4743507", "title": "2025 Annual Global Market Outlook: The Mechazilla Moment", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2070763900/image_2070763900.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Data Patterns Emerging Over Europe - Dark, Blue - Analyzing Global Data Flow, Business, Technology\" data-id=\"2070763900\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2070763900/image_2070763900.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2070763900/image_2070763900.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2070763900/image_2070763900.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2070763900/image_2070763900.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2070763900/image_2070763900.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2070763900/image_2070763900.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2070763900/image_2070763900.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2070763900/image_2070763900.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">DKosig</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>An enduring image from 2024 will be the capture of the SpaceX booster rocket by the Mechazilla robot arms on its return to Earth. This achievement served as a powerful metaphor for the year: the improbable not only became possible but</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2070763900/image_2070763900.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743507-2025-annual-global-market-outlook-mechazilla-moment", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 12:00:00"}, {"id": "4743496", "title": "American Outdoor Brands Delivers A Knockout Quarter: Well In The Buy Zone", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305448692/image_1305448692.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Shot of a cute vintage teapot in a campsite near to lake.\" data-id=\"1305448692\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305448692/image_1305448692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305448692/image_1305448692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305448692/image_1305448692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305448692/image_1305448692.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305448692/image_1305448692.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305448692/image_1305448692.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305448692/image_1305448692.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305448692/image_1305448692.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">ArtistGNDphotography</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>American Outdoor Brands (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AOUT\" title=\"American Outdoor Brands, Inc.\">AOUT</a></span>) is a $180 million, Missouri-based company situated in the outdoor lifestyle space. In 2020, the company was <a href=\"https://ir.smith-wesson.com/news-releases/news-release-details/smith-wesson-brands-inc-completes-spin-american-outdoor-brands\" rel=\"nofollow\">spun off</a> from the weapons manufacturer, Smith &amp; Wesson (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SWBI\" title=\"Smith &amp; Wesson Brands, Inc.\">SWBI</a>). Today, it boasts a</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305448692/image_1305448692.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743496-american-outdoor-brands-delivers-a-knockout-quarter-well-in-the-buy-zone", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 11:47:38"}, {"id": "4743493", "title": "Legacy Housing: Unlocking The Value Of Hidden Assets", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1051469438/image_1051469438.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A tiny house with large glass windows, sits in the backyard, surrounded by a wooden fence and trees.\" data-id=\"1051469438\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1051469438/image_1051469438.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1051469438/image_1051469438.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1051469438/image_1051469438.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1051469438/image_1051469438.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1051469438/image_1051469438.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1051469438/image_1051469438.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1051469438/image_1051469438.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1051469438/image_1051469438.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Mireya Acierto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Back in April, I published <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4683706-legacy-housing-getting-ready-for-a-comeback\">a piece</a> on tiny home builder Legacy Housing Corp. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LEGH\" title=\"Legacy Housing Corporation\">LEGH</a></span>) wherein I pointed out that the company and the housing industry in general were in the throes of a housing</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1051469438/image_1051469438.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743493-legacy-housing-unlocking-the-value-of-hidden-assets", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 11:34:46"}, {"id": "4743490", "title": "Stitch Fix Earnings: A Strong Quarter, But Risks Remain (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/959367958/image_959367958.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Laughing friends looking at tops in mirror during shopping trip in clothing boutique\" data-id=\"959367958\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/959367958/image_959367958.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/959367958/image_959367958.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/959367958/image_959367958.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/959367958/image_959367958.jpg?io=getty-c-w75